; Budget report should not crash when budget accounts contain multiple commodities.
; Previously, quantity() returned 0 for multi-commodity balances, causing a
; divide-by-zero in the percentage column calculation.

~ Monthly
  Expenses:Food   $200
  Expenses:Stocks  3 AAPL
  Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Grocery Store
  Expenses:Food   $150
  Assets:Checking

2024/01/20 Buy Stock
  Expenses:Stocks  2 AAPL
  Assets:Checking

test budget --period 'January 2024' --flat --no-color
       $-150
     -2 AAPL        $-200
                  -3 AAPL          $50
                                1 AAPL     0  Assets:Checking
        $150         $200         $-50   75%  Expenses:Food
      2 AAPL       3 AAPL      -1 AAPL   67%  Expenses:Stocks
------------ ------------ ------------ -----
           0            0            0     0
end test
